---
/**
 * TL;DR Block Component (AEO)
 * Concise answer block for "Answer-first" content formatting.
 * Designed to be extracted by AI engines and Google Featured Snippets.
 *
 * Usage in MDX:
 * <TldrBlock>
 *   The concise answer to the main question of this article goes here.
 *   Keep it under 2-3 sentences for maximum snippet capture rate.
 * </TldrBlock>
 */
---

<aside
  class="tldr-block bg-info/10 border-info my-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 p-5"
  role="note"
  aria-label="TL;DR"
>
  <p class="text-info mt-0 mb-2 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">TL;DR</p>
  <div class="text-foreground text-base leading-relaxed [&>p]:my-0">
    <slot />
  </div>
</aside>
